extends the\nresult to provide a set of criteria for the n-twisted double of a general knot\nK to be slice; that is, of order 0 in C.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 4 Jun 2012 16:33:59 GMT"}],"update_date":"2012-06-05"}
