osition of metadata-guided\nautomatically modified modules representing altered protein binding sites.\nPetri nets composed from modules can be executed as ODE system, stochastic,\nhybrid, or merely qualitative models and exported in SMBL format.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 5 Jun 2012 15:21:49 GMT"}],"update_date":"2012-06-06"}
